        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/edb3f5/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-08-17T20:10:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Interesting article in Vinography by Alder Yarrow on the Savoie wines of Domaine Curtet:</p><aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.vinography.com/2021/08/the-forest-dreams-of-the-savoie-vine-the-wines-of-domaine-curtet\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/a/9/a9e0b2af6c9d420f940db99e287c26f623c811d4.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.vinography.com/2021/08/the-forest-dreams-of-the-savoie-vine-the-wines-of-domaine-curtet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"05:00PM - 14 August 2021\">Vinography \u2013 14 Aug 21</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:666/500;\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/f/3f3c125e2d0049d512fac3ec840d59c06d254f2c_2_666x500.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/f/3f3c125e2d0049d512fac3ec840d59c06d254f2c_2_666x500.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/f/3f3c125e2d0049d512fac3ec840d59c06d254f2c_2_999x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/3/f/3f3c125e2d0049d512fac3ec840d59c06d254f2c.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"6F8A43\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.vinography.com/2021/08/the-forest-dreams-of-the-savoie-vine-the-wines-of-domaine-curtet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">The Forest Dreams of the Savoie Vine: The Wines of Domaine Curtet : Vinography</a></h3>\n\n  <p>An explanation and overview of the wines of Domaine Curtet from the Savoie region of France with tasting notes and scores for their wines.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n<p>\nwho sounds a bit like he farms by Fukuoka, or one step beyond that. He\u2019s working w/ an interesting selection<br>\nof Savoie varieties. He wants to eventually grow all the genetic relatives of Mondeuse. He rejects many of the<br>\ntenents of farming BioDynamic as contrived &amp; artificial. He\u2019s a \u201cnatural\u201d winemakers but rejects the idea of any<br>\nmousey character in his wines. That\u2019s a bit shocking.</p>\n<p>Anybody tried the Curtet wines?? And?? Production is only around 2500 cs. Don\u2019t know if they\u2019re imported into the US or not.</p>\n<p>Tom</p>",
